00:00:32.110 --> 00:00:35.040
Key Points:
Key Point 1.

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:41.090
Line the ball up with the upper inside part
of your foot, about where the base of your

00:00:41.090 --> 00:00:42.210
toes are.

00:00:42.210 --> 00:00:45.410
The ball should be 7-10 inches away.

00:00:45.410 --> 00:00:50.090
Key Point 2.

00:00:50.090 --> 00:00:57.290
Toe studs on the ball, your heel turned away
from your shin.

00:00:57.290 --> 00:01:07.170
Key Point 3.

00:01:07.170 --> 00:01:10.990
Roll ball across quickly to make it ramp over
your plant foot.

00:01:10.990 --> 00:01:12.699
Key Point 4.

00:01:12.699 --> 00:01:19.130
Bring kicking leg around plant leg with the
inside of your foot facing up to make contact

00:01:19.130 --> 00:01:20.130
and start juggling

00:01:20.130 --> 00:01:24.970
You need a Soccer Ball.

00:01:24.970 --> 00:01:30.269
Soccer Exercise Player Can Do:
Start off practicing the motion of this trick

00:01:30.269 --> 00:01:32.140
first without the ball.

00:01:32.140 --> 00:01:37.240
Once you feel good about your technique the
next step is to break this move into two parts.

00:01:37.240 --> 00:01:41.680
First part is to roll the ball across your
plant foot and get the ball to ramp up over

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:43.050
your foot.

00:01:43.050 --> 00:01:46.380
Once that is going smooth, then do the first
part and add in the second part of bring your

00:01:46.380 --> 00:01:50.420
kicking foot around your plant leg to start
juggling the ball to complete the trick.

00:01:50.420 --> 00:01:54.400
Repeat until you have mastered it.

